zornmesh daemon
Start and manage the local zornmesh daemon.

Usage: zornmesh daemon [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  status    Inspect daemon reachability without starting it
  shutdown  Request graceful daemon shutdown
  help      Print daemon help

Options:
      --config <PATH>        Read CLI defaults from a key=value config file
      --socket <PATH>  Override the local daemon socket path
      --output <FORMAT>      Select human, json, or ndjson output
      --non-interactive      Fail fast instead of prompting
  -h, --help           Print help
